  "prompt": "Where can I find device art generators for Samsung S5?",
  "response": "Device art generators are tools that allow you to create realistic mockups of your app or website on various devices, including smartphones like the Samsung Galaxy S5. Here are some options to find device art generators that support the Samsung S5:\n\n1. **Google's Device Art Generator**: Google provides a tool as part of its Android developer resources that allows you to generate device art images. You can access it at [Android Device Art Generator](https://androidmaterialdesign.com/device-art-generator).\n\n2. **Mockup Tools**: Websites like Placeit, Smartmockups, or Mockup World offer a variety of mockup templates, including for specific devices. You can search for the Samsung Galaxy S5 in their library. \n\n3. **Figma or Adobe XD Resources**: If you're familiar with design tools like Figma or Adobe XD, you can find templates or plugins specifically for device mockups. Check their community resources for any Samsung S5 templates.\n\n4. **Graphic Design Tools**: Apps like Canva and Snappa may provide mockup templates as well. You would typically search their libraries for smartphone mockups.\n\n5. **Photoshop Templates**: If you use Photoshop, you can find free or paid PSD mockup templates that include the Samsung Galaxy S5. Websites like GraphicBurger or CreativeMarket often have these kinds of resources.\n\n6. **Online Search**: A keyword search such as \"Samsung Galaxy S5 device mockup\" or \"Samsung S5 mockup generator\" can yield additional websites or resources that might have what you're looking for.\n\nMake sure to check the license and usage rights if you intend to use these for commercial purposes!",
